text: Desmiphora rufocristata is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Melzer in 1935. It is known from Brazil.BioLib.cz - Desmiphora rufocristata. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Desmiphora Category:Beetles described in 1935
